data.description: AWESOME SAN CARLOS HOME in a great neighborhood. This home is a must see!! With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and many recent updates to improve your comfort living experience. Updates include, but not limited to; Fully-insulated attic with R-30 and most exterior walls with R-13,  All windows upgraded to dual pane, New bathroom faucets, smart kitchen faucet, 2.0 hp InSinkErator, New GE ultra-quiet dishwasher with built in garbage disposal, New Frigidaire electric range, New LED light fixtures, recessed lighting in living room/dining room is hue-and-brightness adjustable, Skylight with solar-powered light installed in master bath, 50-year Owens Corning energy efficient roof updates, this property is the perfect place to call your home! There’s more!! New HVAC (20-22 SEER) with 36 variable-capacity operation and furnace (moved to attic), Tankless Navian water heater, 10 GPM. Additionally, new water pressure regulator, main shutoff valve. And there is a fully paid off 6 KW Solar Panel System!!!! The home also has a Amarr triple-layer insulated garage door with dual-pane windows and LiftMaster smart garage door opener with battery backup, lifetime warranty on all garage door hardware. There are more updates, just too many to list here, come see the home, you’ll love it!! This home is close to schools, shopping, restaurants, and easy access to freeways. Again, this is a must-see home, check it out!!
